   132→## 0.2.10
   133→
   134→- Fixed
   135→  - Raise `TOMLDecodeError` if overwriting nested inline tables from the parent inline
   136→  - Raise `TOMLDecodeError` if escaped Unicode character is not a Unicode scalar value
