   147→## 0.2.8
   148→
   149→- Performance
   150→  - Significant boost to comment parsing speed
   152→## 0.2.7
   153→
   154→- Added
   155→  - Improved `TOMLDecodeError` error messages.
   156→    Line and column are included when applicable.
   158→## 0.2.6
   159→
   160→- Performance
   161→  - Over 5% boost
   163→## 0.2.5
   164→
   165→- Fixed
   166→  - Made exception type `TOMLDecodeError` when overwriting a value with a deeply nested table
   168→## 0.2.4
   169→
   170→- Fixed
   171→  - `TOMLDecodeError` is now raised when attempting to overwrite a value in an inline table's or array's namespace with a table definition
   173→## 0.2.3
   174→
   175→- Fixed
   176→  - Error type was not TOMLDecodeError in some obscure cases
   178→## 0.2.2
   179→
   180→- Added
   181→  - `tomli.load` for parsing IO streams returned by `open()`
   182→  - `parse_float` keyword argument to `tomli.loads`.
   183→    Allows parsing TOML floats to a non-float type in Python.
   185→## 0.2.1
   186→
   187→- Fixed
   188→  - `TOMLDecodeError` is now raised for duplicate keys in inline tables,
   189→    as opposed to silently overriding the previous value
   191→## 0.2.0
   192→
   193→- Changed
   194→  - Project name to Tomli
   195→- Performance
   196→  - A performance boost
   198→## 0.1.0
