tomllib.md
     1→# `tomllib` – Tomli in the standard library
     2→
     3→Tomli was added to the Python standard library in Python 3.11.
    13→## Converting Tomli to tomllib
    14→
    15→### Sync status
    16→
    17→`tomllib` in CPython commit https://github.com/python/cpython/commit/deaf509e8fc6e0363bd6f26d52ad42f976ec42f2
    18→matches Tomli commit https://github.com/hukkin/tomli/commit/7e563eed5286b5d46b8290a9f56a86d955b23a9a
    20→### Steps to convert
    21→
    22→- Move everything in `tomli:src/tomli` to `cpython:Lib/tomllib`. Exclude `py.typed`.
